snippet.title: Wizard's Warp - Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Always wanted to learn how to teleport? Try not to get stuck in a wall! Wizard's Warp, a platformer that challenges those who are not afraid of hard challenges. Get to the top to save your favorite cat! But if you fall down, be ready for a rough landing

Releases Q1 2025

Wishlist on steam!
